Menu_GetWidth
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Menu=>menu/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Syntax:	Menu_GetWidth
Veneer:	<menu_get_width>
#indent

On Entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = Menu object ID
r2 = 23
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = width of menu in OS units
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:		Method returns width of the menu.